## ğŸ¯ Features Included

### âœ… **Authentication & Authorization**
- JWT token-based authentication
- Login/Register forms with validation
- Route guards for protected pages
- Role-based access control (ADMIN/USER)
- Auto-logout on token expiry

### âœ… **User Interface Components**
- **Dashboard** - Welcome page with quick actions
- **Profile** - View and edit user profile
- **User Management** - Admin-only user listing and management
- **Navbar** - Navigation with user menu
- **Responsive Design** - Mobile-friendly Material Design

### âœ… **Technical Features**
- HTTP Interceptor for automatic JWT token injection
- Proxy configuration for backend API calls
- Form validation with Angular Reactive Forms
- Error handling and user feedback
- Material Design components
- TypeScript strict mode

## ğŸ” Default Login Credentials
