## ğŸ”§ API Integration
The Angular app automatically proxies API calls to your Micronaut backend:
- `/api/*` â†’ `http://localhost:8080/api/*`
- `/auth/*` â†’ `http://localhost:8080/auth/*`
- `/login` â†’ `http://localhost:8080/login`

